<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Himak nitak á, ahanchi
 Ta̱kla ka, hatak yoshoba
 Chia hʋt Chihowa hoka
 Ish im ile kʋllochi ná.

[V2]
 Illika imanumpa hosh
 Chekosi chim a̱ya chi̱shke:
 Yohmikma chi shilombish ʋt
 Katima 'k o̱ a̱ya chi̱ cho?

[V3]
 Tofa yokʋt chekosikma,
 Onthʋshtohonla chi̱ hoke
 Chekosikma na̱ waya yʋt
 Hoiyot ʋlhtaha chi̱ hoke.

[V4]
 Chekosikma Chihowa hʋt
 Chi̱ nukha̱klo chatuk kia,
 Ish ahninchi keyu hokma,
 Chissa pulla chi̱ mak oke.

[V5]
 Yohmi ka, himak nitak á,
 Ahanchi ta̱kla pulla ka,
 Hatak yoshoba chia hʋt
 Ʋbanumpa ish haklashke.

[V6]
 Tu̱shpʋt minit ʋb' okhissa,
 Chi nukha̱klo hatuk mak o̱,
 Ik okshilitto ki̱sha ka,
 Chukowʋt chi okcha̱yashke.</lyrics>
<aka>Himak nitak á, ahanchi</aka>
<time_sig>L.M. 8.8.8.8.</time_sig>
<title>The Sinner warned ƲIT25</title>
<hymn_number>25</hymn_number>
</song>